item.title: CVE-2023-5980|2023-12-26T18:33:13.444Z -- unknown -- bsk%20forms%20blacklist
item.description: The BSK Forms Blacklist WordPress plugin before 3.7 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup).
